The objective of this test is to observe the Likelihood distribution of parts of speech tags in Sinhala text corpus and understand which tags are most likely to appear. Table III contains tag distribution obtained from the corpus. Tag frequency and number of distinct words with respect to each tag were counted from the corpus. The Likelihood Estimates were calculated for each tag based on number of occurrences of the tag appeared in the corpus against total number of tags in the corpus.
